    "type": "text",
    "content": "Scotland is a <strong>country</strong> located in the <strong>northern part</strong> of the <strong>United Kingdom</strong>. It shares a <strong>land border</strong> with <strong>England</strong> to the south and is otherwise surrounded by the <strong>Atlantic Ocean</strong>, the <strong>North Sea</strong>, and the <strong>Irish Sea</strong>. Scotland is made up of the <strong>mainland</strong> and more than <strong>790 islands</strong>, including the <strong>Hebrides</strong>, <strong>Orkney</strong>, and <strong>Shetland</strong> islands.</p><p>",
