    "paragraph": 2,
    "type": "text",
    "content": "The <strong>capital city</strong> of Scotland is <strong>Edinburgh</strong>, known for its <strong>historic architecture</strong>, <strong>Edinburgh Castle</strong>, and the <strong>Royal Mile</strong>. Edinburgh hosts the world-famous <strong>Edinburgh Festival Fringe</strong>, which is the largest <strong>arts festival</strong> in the world. The largest city is <strong>Glasgow</strong>, a cultural hub for <strong>music</strong>, <strong>art</strong>, and <strong>design</strong>. Other notable cities include <strong>Aberdeen</strong>, <strong>Dundee</strong>, and <strong>Inverness</strong>.</p><p>",
